    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she is a total beauty! This car has been my baby\u2014always garage-kept, meticulously detailed, and it honestly feels like it just left the showroom floor. It\u2019s in such incredible, pristine shape that you\u2019d swear it was brand new. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved and pampered, this is definitely the one for you. I\u2019m so excited for someone else to get behind the wheel and enjoy it as much as I have! Come swing by and see this gem for yourself\u2014you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 43500.0,
