    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 997.2 Carrera S is a definitive example of precision engineering, featuring the 3.8L naturally aspirated flat-six with Direct Fuel Injection (DFI) delivering a linear power band and 385 hp. The chassis remains incredibly rigid, augmented by Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) and the Sport Chrono Package for sharpened throttle response and dynamic engine mounts. Every mechanical component\u2014from the impeccably tight synchros in the 6-speed manual gearbox to the pristine underside and original cross-drilled rotors\u2014reflects a life of fastidious climate-controlled storage and preventative maintenance. The paint depth is consistent across all panels, and the interior retains its factory-fresh tactile feedback. This is a turn-key, investment-grade specimen for the discerning driver.",
